&lt;p&gt;Jumia&amp;nbsp;is a leading pan-African e-commerce platform. Its mission is to improve the quality of everyday life in Africa by leveraging technology to deliver innovative, convenient and affordable online services to customers, while helping businesses grow as they use Jumia&#39;s platform to better reach and serve customers.&lt;/p&gt;
