&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to understand business challenges and contribute to data-driven solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform exploratory data analysis on topics such as customer behavior, search optimization, catalog management, finance, and commercial performance.&lt;/li&gt;
