&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills and the ability to work collaboratively in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Eagerness to learn, take initiative, and contribute to impactful projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
